		<h3 class="article-title">
			<a href="/a/94.html" >宁夏博物馆五一假期开展“向劳动者致敬”系列社教活动</a>
		</h3>
		<span class="article-data" itemprop="date">2018.05.11</span>
	</div>
	
	<div class="article-body">
				<div class="article-left">
